      "message": "If you stick with mvn38 you will need to convince LF to upgrade the version of maven-3.8 installed in the build node. \nCurrently Maven v.3.8.2 is installed for profile 'mvn38', whereas v.3.8.3 is needed by maven plugin org.opendaylight.odlparent:copy-files-plugin:13.0.10 \nI just thought mvn39 might be easier :-)",
